  "source": "[\\set.theoretic.intersection:of{A}:and{B}]\nDefines: I := \\set.theoretic.intersection:over{\\set.theoretic.pair:of{A}:and{B}} is \\set\nwhen: A, B is \\set\nDocumented:\n. called: \"intersection of $A?$ and $B?$\"\n. written: \"A? \\cap B?\"\n. description: \"The intersection $A \\cap B$, defined as the intersection over the collection $\\{A, B\\}$, so that $x \\in A \\cap B$ if and only if $x \\in A$ and $x \\in B$.\"\nId: \"c1766d97-e27d-4e5f-8d60-6621c1b0ca68\"",
